#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.read_lance.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.read\\_lance"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.read_lance.read_lance:1 of
msgid "Load a Lance dataset from the file path, returning a DataFrame."
msgstr "从文件路径加载 Lance 数据集，返回 DataFrame。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.read_lance.read_lance of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.read_lance.read_lance:3 of
msgid ""
"Any valid string path is acceptable. The string could be a URL. For "
"Aliyun OSS URLs, the format is: ``oss://<endpoint>/<bucket>/<path>``. "
"Example: ``oss://oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/my-bucket/dataset``. For S3 "
"URLs, the format is: ``s3://<bucket>/<path>``."
msgstr ""
"任何有效的字符串路径都是可接受的。字符串可以是 URL。对于阿里云 OSS URL，"
"格式为：``oss://<endpoint>/<bucket>/<path>``。示例：``oss://oss-cn-"
"beijing.aliyuncs.com/my-bucket/dataset``。对于 S3 URL，格式为：``s3://<"
"bucket>/<path>``。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.read_lance.read_lance:8 of
msgid ""
"Specific version of the dataset to read. If not specified, reads the "
"latest version."
msgstr "要读取的数据集的特定版本。如果未指定，则读取最新版本。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.read_lance.read_lance:11 of
msgid ""
"Timestamp for point-in-time read. Format: ISO 8601 datetime string. "
"Cannot be used together with version."
msgstr ""
"时间点读取的时间戳。格式：ISO 8601 日期时间字符串。不能与 version 参数"
"一起使用。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.read_lance.read_lance:14 of
msgid "If not None, only these columns will be read from the dataset."
msgstr "如果不为 None，则只从数据集中读取这些列。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.read_lance.read_lance:16 of
msgid ""
"SQL-like filter expression for predicate pushdown. The filter is applied "
"during read to filter rows within each fragment. Example: ``\"age > 18 "
"AND city = 'Beijing'\"``"
msgstr ""
"用于谓词下推的类 SQL 过滤表达式。过滤器在读取期间应用，以过滤每个片段中的"
"行。示例：``\"age > 18 AND city = 'Beijing'\"``"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.read_lance.read_lance:20 of
msgid ""
"Column(s) to use as the row labels of the DataFrame, either given as "
"string name or column index. If a sequence of int/str is given, a "
"MultiIndex is used. If False, no column is used as index (ignoring any "
"pandas metadata in the dataset). If None, uses pandas metadata if "
"available, otherwise falls back to default_index_type."
msgstr ""
"用作 DataFrame 行标签的列，可以是字符串名称或列索引。如果给定了 int/str "
"序列，则使用 MultiIndex。如果为 False，则不使用任何列作为索引（忽略数据"
"集中的任何 pandas 元数据）。如果为 None，则在可用时使用 pandas 元数据，"
"否则回退到 default_index_type。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.read_lance.read_lance:26 of
msgid ""
"If index_col not specified, specify type of index to generate. If not "
"specified, `options.dataframe.default_index_type` will be used."
msgstr ""
"如果未指定 index_col，则指定要生成的索引类型。如果未指定，将使用 `options"
".dataframe.default_index_type`。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.read_lance.read_lance:29 of
msgid "Back-end data type applied to the resultant DataFrame."
msgstr "应用于结果 DataFrame 的后端数据类型。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.read_lance.read_lance:31 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Options for storage connection. For Aliyun OSS with RAM role: "
"``{'role_arn': 'acs:ram::xxx:role/name'}`` For Aliyun OSS with AK/SK: "
"``{'access_key_id': 'xxx', 'access_key_secret': 'xxx'}`` For S3: "
"``{'aws_access_key_id': 'xxx', 'aws_secret_access_key': 'xxx'}``"
msgstr ""
"存储连接选项。对于使用 RAM 角色的阿里云 OSS：``{'role_arn': 'acs:ram::xxx"
":role/name'}`` 对于使用 AK/SK 的阿里云 OSS：``{'access_key_id': 'xxx', '"
"access_key_secret': 'xxx'}`` 对于 S3：``{'aws_access_key_id': 'xxx', 'aws"
"_secret_access_key': 'xxx'}``"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.read_lance.read_lance:36 of
msgid "Scale that real memory occupation divided with raw file size."
msgstr "实际内存占用除以原始文件大小的比例。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.read_lance.read_lance:38 of
msgid ""
"Merge small Lance fragments into larger chunks for better parallel "
"processing efficiency."
msgstr "将小的 Lance 片段合并为更大的块，以获得更好的并行处理效率。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.read_lance.read_lance:41 of
msgid "Options for merging small files."
msgstr "合并小文件的选项。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.read_lance.read_lance:43 of
msgid "Any additional kwargs are passed to lance."
msgstr "任何额外的 kwargs 都会传递给 lance。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.read_lance.read_lance of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

